title: Billion Dollar Babies (former members of Alice Cooper) - Battle
description:
Vinyl Rip

This is (the REAL) Billion Dollar Babies with Michael Bruce, Dennis Dunaway, Neal Smith (all three former members of the original Alice Cooper band), Bob Dolin and Mike Marconi.

I&#039;m not sure if I have made the right "cut" on the 3-4 last songs - but anyway here it is!
